<br>
Agro has so many facets, only one of which is weapon proc. Consider also who hits the mob first, whether the monk feigned and stayed down for clean transfer.  Which silly caster is sitting nearby.  Which suicidal shaman malo'd on the pull or cannied below two bubbles.  Which chanter landed + agro on you just after you tagged the mob.  Whether you tanked the mob alone for a bit or your band of killers jumped right in.  <br>
<br>
Done right, you should be able to tank with a rusty nail and hold agro.   <p><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=9666 ">Bonehammer</a><BR>Warlord of Phantom Raiders<BR>Bertoxxulous</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=2163.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=2163.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2163.topic&index=41><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=2163.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=2163.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2163.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2163.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriortheare